1
00:00:13,960 --> 00:00:15,320
Are you in a hurry to leave?

2
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:22,640
I have to be back before nine.

3
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:24,640
Zhai Qiuyu wants me to give him a massage.

4
00:00:26,160 --> 00:00:27,199
I knew it.

5
00:00:28,120 --> 00:00:29,480
He's not that kind of nice.

6
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:36,640
Li Youen

7
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:39,840
Do you like Zhai Qiuyu?

8
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:47,880
Teacher Zhou

9
00:00:48,359 --> 00:00:49,359
You've misunderstood.

10
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:53,079
Zhai Qiuyu

11
00:00:53,759 --> 00:00:55,119
He's a very good boss.

12
00:00:55,799 --> 00:00:57,039
Just a boss?

13
00:00:59,719 --> 00:01:01,280
You really should let him hear this.

14
00:01:02,479 --> 00:01:04,200
See if he can still sit still.

15
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:09,560
Teacher Zhou,

16
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:12,000
Then I'll ask another question.

17
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,359
Zhai Qiuyu

18
00:01:15,879 --> 00:01:17,640
Would you kiss other employees too?

19
00:01:27,319 --> 00:01:29,200
You know how he feels about you.

20
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,480
Why won't you admit it?

21
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:35,319
What are you worried about?

22
00:01:36,359 --> 00:01:37,359
I'm not.

23
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,799
Are you scared?

24
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:46,439
Are you afraid of guessing his thoughts wrong?

25
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:50,000
Or afraid he's just acting on impulse?

26
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:53,799
This guy,

27
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,719
he never had many friends growing up.

28
00:01:56,439 --> 00:01:57,920
He never liked interacting with people.

29
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,719
He'd shut himself in the sports field all day,

30
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,560
like a bird in a cage,

31
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,319
a fish in a tank.

32
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:05,599
No different, really.

33
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,840
But it's different now.

34
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:14,280
This is the first time I've seen

35
00:02:15,039 --> 00:02:16,680
him so close with someone.

36
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:18,919
Living together,

37
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:20,919
going everywhere together.

38
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,719
Li Youen.

39
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,960
Do you know who I'm talking about?

40
00:02:40,199 --> 00:02:41,560
It's not time yet.

41
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,560
You're already so impatient?

42
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,240
Answer it.

43
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:47,960
If you don't answer,

44
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:50,120
he'll break in.

45
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,280
Zhai Qiuyu.

46
00:02:59,439 --> 00:03:00,280
Come out.

47
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,680
I'll take you to the club.

48
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,840
There's a last-minute meeting.

49
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,079
Zhai Qiuyu

50
00:04:54,199 --> 00:04:55,360
I'm not discussing this with you.

51
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,240
A partial tendon tear.

52
00:04:58,319 --> 00:04:59,480
There are signs of fibrosis.

53
00:05:00,079 --> 00:05:00,920
If you play again,

54
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:03,000
it won't just be three months of rest.

55
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:04,600
You're immediately suspended.

56
00:05:05,079 --> 00:05:05,720
Otherwise,

57
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,720
your career will be over.

58
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,319
You've made it through so many years.

59
00:05:10,079 --> 00:05:10,759
It's just pain.

60
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,319
I can endure it.

61
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:17,040
Is this a matter of enduring it?

62
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,480
This is a lifelong matter.

63
00:05:21,639 --> 00:05:22,519
I already said,

64
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,040
I can play.

65
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,000
Teacher Li

66
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:30,600
Come out with me for a moment.

67
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:45,120
I know Qiuyu's personality too well.

68
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,439
He's as stubborn as a mule.

69
00:05:47,439 --> 00:05:48,879
He definitely won't agree to rest.

70
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:51,120
We need to think of another way.

71
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:53,680
But if things continue on this path,

72
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,560
his elbow

73
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,920
might need surgery.

74
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,240
You have to help me persuade him.

75
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,439
Make sure he rests this weekend.

76
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,800
He'll listen to you.

77
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,120
I'll do my best.

78
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:15,319
Your stuff

79
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,240
I'll give it back

80
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,639
What did you and Zhou Song

81
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:35,800
talk about?

82
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,000
If I told you,

83
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,040
could you grant me a wish?

84
00:06:47,879 --> 00:06:48,639
Sure.

85
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,759
He said,

86
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,040
'You have a bad temper'

87
00:06:54,439 --> 00:06:55,439
'and I should be careful.'

88
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,560
You scoundrel

89
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,199
up to no good again

90
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,360
Teacher Zhou

91
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:25,879
where are you?

92
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,639
Drowning your sorrows?

93
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,480
What's wrong, Gu Hao?

94
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,800
Are you going to join me for a couple of drinks?

95
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:36,680
It really is you!

96
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,360
Teacher Zhou

97
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:39,360
Why are you drinking here alone?

98
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,639
How did you get out of the phone?

99
00:07:43,319 --> 00:07:45,000
I was watching over there for a long time.

100
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,639
I thought I was seeing things.

101
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:52,680
Are you here to drink alone too?

102
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:55,120
I just finished drinking with my seniors from the Photography Club.

103
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:04,000
So you're not drinking alone.

104
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,800
Teacher Zhou,

105
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,600
Aren't you happy?

106
00:08:27,759 --> 00:08:28,319
No,

107
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,240
I just realized

108
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:33,840
I'm not special enough.

109
00:08:36,879 --> 00:08:37,799
How could that be?

110
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:40,440
You've always been a very special person.

111
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:44,000
So sensitive, focused, and diligent.

112
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:46,240
You can sense everyone's emotions.

113
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:48,000
Just like when you took photos of Teacher Li.

114
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:48,799
That angle,

115
00:08:48,799 --> 00:08:49,559
that atmosphere,

116
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:51,440
it could beat everyone in our club.

117
00:08:51,879 --> 00:08:52,679
And also,

118
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:53,919
that little figure you sculpted,

119
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,039
it was so well-made,

120
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,559
exactly like my cousin's kid.

121
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,679
You didn't pop that big snot bubble

122
00:09:02,559 --> 00:09:03,360
Thank you

123
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:09,120
I'm feeling much better now

124
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,200
Then why is the corner of your mouth

125
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,919
always turned down like that

126
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,120
That looks much better

127
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:23,559
You've had too much to drink

128
00:09:24,559 --> 00:09:25,639
You should go back early

129
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,200
I haven't

130
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:29,120
I've wanted to tell you this for a long time

131
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,799
I just didn't dare to

132
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,919
From the very first moment I saw you,

133
00:09:36,919 --> 00:09:39,000
I felt you were someone special.

134
00:09:40,639 --> 00:09:42,799
Even though I don't know what you went through today,

135
00:09:43,879 --> 00:09:45,360
I still want to tell you:

136
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,120
In my heart,

137
00:09:47,879 --> 00:09:48,559
you will always be

138
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:50,000
someone I want to be close to.

139
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,360
Close to me for what?

140
00:09:52,879 --> 00:09:53,799
Little Gu Hao,

141
00:09:54,639 --> 00:09:56,039
you don't know me well enough yet.

142
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,240
I'm not exactly a good person.

143
00:10:02,759 --> 00:10:03,639
You're not good

144
00:10:05,279 --> 00:10:06,360
How bad could you be?

145
00:10:26,519 --> 00:10:27,759
This girl

146
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:30,679
She definitely wasn't feeling this way then

147
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,240
Let's help her

148
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:37,159
Boss

149
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,159
Boss

150
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:40,759
Boss

151
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,759
Boss

152
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:45,000
If you don't come out, we're stealing

153
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:47,600
Boss!

154
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,879
If you don't come out, we're going to steal something!

155
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:51,840
Boss!

156
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,000
Boss!

157
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,240
Boss!

158
00:10:56,559 --> 00:10:57,399
Zhou Song?

159
00:10:58,159 --> 00:10:59,240
There's no one here.

160
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,200
Do you have any change?

161
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,399
Let's go.

162
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:47,840
It seems to be

163
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:49,759
glowing.

164
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:56,240
Close your eyes

165
00:11:58,879 --> 00:11:59,720
Feel it

166
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:02,720
The edges

167
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:04,840
The cracks

168
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:09,159
I don't like things that are too perfect

169
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:21,840
Come

170
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:46,000
Later

171
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:48,360
I want to try blending

172
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,679
softness and strength

173
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:53,120
but I've never been able to achieve

174
00:12:53,759 --> 00:12:55,000
the results I want

175
00:13:00,639 --> 00:13:01,159
This

176
00:13:02,279 --> 00:13:04,120
is the clay that just arrived today.

177
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,360
It's still breathing,

178
00:13:07,759 --> 00:13:09,399
waiting to be shaped.

179
00:13:19,799 --> 00:13:20,600
Now,

180
00:13:21,759 --> 00:13:23,000
their sum

181
00:13:24,639 --> 00:13:25,759
is right here.

182
00:13:45,159 --> 00:13:46,519
Are you sure about this?

183
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:54,240
Don't you like it?

184
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:07,000
I like it.

185
00:14:10,639 --> 00:14:12,159
It's precisely because I like you

186
00:14:12,879 --> 00:14:14,480
that I can't touch you recklessly

187
00:14:15,759 --> 00:14:16,879
to avoid embarrassment

188
00:14:36,279 --> 00:14:37,240
Breakfast is ready

189
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,120
I'll eat after I get back from training

190
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:46,360
What are you doing?

191
00:14:46,759 --> 00:14:47,480
Competitor Zhai

192
00:14:47,759 --> 00:14:49,000
You need to rest now

193
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:50,360
instead of training even harder

194
00:14:53,879 --> 00:14:55,519
You know my competition is coming up soon, right?

195
00:14:56,519 --> 00:14:57,840
Today is a rest day

196
00:15:01,279 --> 00:15:03,399
I want to use that wish I had before

197
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:31,759
Use a rosy hue

198
00:15:32,519 --> 00:15:34,279
Most people use sappanwood as a dye

199
00:15:36,759 --> 00:15:38,120
Try stirring it

200
00:15:38,639 --> 00:15:39,360
No

201
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:44,720
Just try it

202
00:15:48,879 --> 00:15:50,759
A deep red color is fine

203
00:16:10,759 --> 00:16:11,240
It's done

204
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:11,879
Li Youen

205
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:18,639
Tie-dyeing needs steps

206
00:16:18,639 --> 00:16:19,639
You can't rush it like this

207
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:21,240
As long as it dyes, isn't that enough?

208
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:27,080
I already said you can't rush this.

209
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:33,080
Let me do it.

210
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:34,639
No, no, it's fine.

211
00:16:34,639 --> 00:16:35,320
I'll do it.

212
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:42,399
You can't dye it like this.

213
00:16:42,639 --> 00:16:43,759
The colors won't come out right.

214
00:16:44,480 --> 00:16:45,240
They won't?

215
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:48,399
Then I guess I'm a pioneer.

216
00:16:52,799 --> 00:16:53,399
Your...

217
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:57,879
The colors are all ruined.

218
00:16:58,519 --> 00:16:59,039
You...

219
00:17:09,279 --> 00:17:10,079
What are you afraid of?

220
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:12,480
We're all just here to have fun anyway.

221
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:14,039
If we're going to play,

222
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:16,119
we might as well go all out.

223
00:17:38,599 --> 00:17:39,720
It's not that big of a deal.

224
00:17:40,119 --> 00:17:42,240
Next time, help me check how it's dyed.

225
00:17:45,119 --> 00:17:46,160
I'm going to take a bath.

226
00:17:56,759 --> 00:17:57,400
Come in!

227
00:18:20,759 --> 00:18:22,079
You splashed me!

228
00:18:29,359 --> 00:18:30,240
Zhai Qiuyu

229
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:06,559
Li Youen

230
00:19:07,559 --> 00:19:08,680
Let's kiss again.

231
00:21:11,559 --> 00:21:13,079
You've been doing laundry for so long.

232
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:22,839
I...

233
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:25,880
Hurry up!

234
00:21:44,359 --> 00:21:45,160
Xiao Si,

235
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:46,039
Brother,

236
00:21:46,039 --> 00:21:47,640
Look what delicious food I brought you.

237
00:21:52,359 --> 00:21:53,680
What kind of day is it today?

238
00:21:53,799 --> 00:21:54,880
So much delicious food!

239
00:22:29,559 --> 00:22:30,680
It's going to overflow, Brother!

240
00:22:49,640 --> 00:22:50,119
Brother,

241
00:22:50,400 --> 00:22:51,559
Who are you texting?

242
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:53,559
A friend?

243
00:22:56,400 --> 00:22:57,640
Your girlfriend?

244
00:23:00,440 --> 00:23:01,279
No.

245
00:23:02,079 --> 00:23:03,119
Not my girlfriend.

246
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,279
She's really my girlfriend!

247
00:23:08,359 --> 00:23:09,400
Not really.

248
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:11,319
He just

249
00:23:12,000 --> 00:23:14,000
punished those who bullied me.

250
00:23:14,359 --> 00:23:17,160
It was just when no one else believed in me,

251
00:23:17,720 --> 00:23:18,920
that he stood up for me.

252
00:23:19,240 --> 00:23:20,119
I can prove it.

253
00:23:23,799 --> 00:23:25,400
He stayed with me all day yesterday.

254
00:23:26,640 --> 00:23:27,920
That's not all.

255
00:23:30,119 --> 00:23:31,079
And

256
00:23:31,519 --> 00:23:32,599
should we just let it go?

257
00:23:32,599 --> 00:23:33,599
Of course, we should.

258
00:23:33,799 --> 00:23:35,599
This girl is too kind.

259
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:38,119
When can you bring her to meet me?

260
00:23:41,559 --> 00:23:42,319
Later,

261
00:23:42,319 --> 00:23:43,279
we'll see.

262
00:23:44,400 --> 00:23:45,640
I'm off to work now.

263
00:23:46,440 --> 00:23:46,960
Brother,

264
00:23:47,359 --> 00:23:49,119
remember to bring sister-in-law to see me.

265
00:24:33,119 --> 00:24:35,839
They're a typical defensive counter-attack team.

266
00:24:36,519 --> 00:24:37,160
Steady pace.

267
00:24:37,519 --> 00:24:38,400
Low error rate.

268
00:24:38,799 --> 00:24:40,160
To break through their defense,

269
00:24:40,559 --> 00:24:42,599
we need stronger offensive pressure.

270
00:24:43,079 --> 00:24:44,640
Especially on serves and at the net.

271
00:24:44,839 --> 00:24:45,400
Zhai Qiuyu,

272
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:47,200
your power and speed are key.

273
00:24:47,920 --> 00:24:50,119
Li Ran has been imitating this defensive style lately.

274
00:24:50,359 --> 00:24:51,200
These next few days,

275
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:52,880
you two can practice against each other.

276
00:24:53,079 --> 00:24:53,960
Help each other find your form.

277
00:24:54,119 --> 00:24:55,319
No problem, Coach Wang.

278
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:05,799
Our goal is the same:

279
00:25:06,079 --> 00:25:07,119
to defeat our opponents.

280
00:25:07,279 --> 00:25:08,359
The championship is ours.

281
00:25:08,839 --> 00:25:09,960
Well said.

282
00:25:10,799 --> 00:25:12,119
I have good news for everyone.

283
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:14,440
Our club has just won

284
00:25:14,440 --> 00:25:17,119
the Professional Tennis Club of the Year Gold Award again.

285
00:25:17,559 --> 00:25:19,279
I'll take you all to a hot spring this weekend.

286
00:25:20,119 --> 00:25:21,319
Great!

287
00:25:22,720 --> 00:25:23,559
I'm not going.

288
00:25:24,559 --> 00:25:25,200
Qiu Yu,

289
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:26,400
look at you.

290
00:25:27,559 --> 00:25:28,200
Teacher Li.

291
00:25:31,039 --> 00:25:31,680
Yes

292
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:35,079
Soaking in hot springs can help relieve

293
00:25:35,079 --> 00:25:38,039
